IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. DIRECTIONAL-ARITHMETIC.

DATA DIVISION.
01 A PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 B PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 C PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 D PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 E PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 F PICTURE IS 9(3).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE 10 TO A
MOVE 30 TO B
MOVE 30 TO E
MOVE 25 TO F
SUBTRACT A FROM B GIVING C
DIVIDE A INTO B GIVING D
SUBTRACT 5 FROM E
DIVIDE 5 INTO F
STOP.
